quiz.question:
Which image will the following code produce?

```python
from byubit import Bit


def turn(bit):
    bit.left()
    bit.move()
    bit.left()


@Bit.empty_world(5, 3)
def run(bit):
    while bit.front_clear():
        bit.move()
        bit.paint('green')
    turn(bit)
    while bit.front_clear():
        bit.move()
        bit.paint('blue')

if __name__ == '__main__':
    run(Bit.new_bit)
```
